# Pew dbt router overlay

Extends [agent-router-base](agent-router-base.mdc). Invoke specialists **explicitly** in the prompt when possible; this table is the fallback.

## Task → agent mapping

| Task | Primary agent | Also invoke when applicable |
|------|---------------|----------------------------|
| Edit SQL models | [agent-model-change](agent-model-change.mdc) | [agent-incremental-safety](agent-incremental-safety.mdc) if incremental; [agent-dashboard-impact](agent-dashboard-impact.mdc) if marts/reporting |
| Review PR or diff | [agent-pr-reviewer](agent-pr-reviewer.mdc) | [agent-dashboard-impact](agent-dashboard-impact.mdc), [safe-change-review](safe-change-review.mdc) |
| Incremental logic / config | [agent-incremental-safety](agent-incremental-safety.mdc) | [agent-model-change](agent-model-change.mdc) |
| Marts, exposures, TOP, quarterly KPIs | [agent-dashboard-impact](agent-dashboard-impact.mdc) | [safe-change-review](safe-change-review.mdc) |
| Identity, segments, SFMC/GA4 joins | [agent-segmentation-identity](agent-segmentation-identity.mdc) | [agent-dashboard-impact](agent-dashboard-impact.mdc) if DDM dashboards |
| Materialization or model deletion | [agent-materialization-review](agent-materialization-review.mdc) | [agent-dashboard-impact](agent-dashboard-impact.mdc) |
| Docs only | [agent-documentation](agent-documentation.mdc) | — |
| Validate a claim before changing code | [agent-audit](agent-audit.mdc) | relevant specialist for the domain |
| YAML tests / schema YAML | [agent-test-yaml](agent-test-yaml.mdc) | [safe-change-review](safe-change-review.mdc) if grain changes |
| Source freshness | [agent-source-freshness](agent-source-freshness.mdc) | — |

## Repo agent supplements

- PR review: [pew-dbt-pr-reviewer-overlay](pew-dbt-pr-reviewer-overlay.mdc)
- Audit: [pew-dbt-audit-overlay](pew-dbt-audit-overlay.mdc)

## Shared rules (`alwaysApply: true`)

- [analytics-context](analytics-context.mdc) — repo stack and orientation
- [agent-router-base](agent-router-base.mdc) — global routing principles
- [safe-change-review](safe-change-review.mdc) — consumer checks, plan-before-edit gate
- [pew-dbt-high-risk](pew-dbt-high-risk.mdc) — Pew high-risk areas and runbooks
- [dbt-validation-commands](dbt-validation-commands.mdc) — canonical `dbt` commands
- [agent-output-contract](agent-output-contract.mdc) — response shape and no-fake-inspection rules

## Example prompts

**Model change:**
```text
Use agent-model-change and agent-incremental-safety.
Investigate [issue] in mart_content_daily.
Map upstream/downstream, state grain, classify the change.
Do not edit until you propose the smallest safe PR.
```

**PR review:**
```text
Use agent-pr-reviewer, agent-dashboard-impact, and safe-change-review.
Review the current diff as a skeptical dbt maintainer.
Focus on metric risk, dashboard breakage, incremental safety, validation gaps.
Return a merge verdict.
```
